    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stones used for rubbing or otherwise applying friction to another surface. Examples of use are for smoothing tiles or other surfaces, sanding or burnishing surfaces, treating animal skins, or processing grain or pigments.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
